    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770206525</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">What in the World Is That?</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Was in der Welt ist das?</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Qu'est-ce que c'est dans le monde ?</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Que no mundo é aquele?</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Che cosa nel mondo è quello?</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Τι στον κόσμο είναι αυτός;</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">¿Cuál en el mundo es ése?</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">examines 16 inventions: the submarine, battery radio, cotton gin, reaper, electron microscope, telephone, gramophone, telecommunication cable, snow gauge, ornithopter, airphibian, and others.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">überprüft 16 Erfindungen: das Unterseeboot, der 
Batterieradio, die Entkörnungsmaschine, das reaper, das 
Elektronenmikroskop, das Telefon, das Grammophon, das 
Telekommunikationkabel, die Schnelehre, das ornithopter, das 
airphibian und andere.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">examine 16 inventions : le sous-marin, la radio de 
batterie, le genièvre de coton, la moissonneuse, le microscope 
électronique, le téléphone, le phonographe, le câble de 
télécommunication, la mesure de neige, l'ornithopter, l'airphibian, 
et d'autres.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">examina 16 invenções: o submarino, o rádio da 
bateria, o gin de algodão, o reaper, o microscópio de elétron, o 
telefone, o gramophone, o cabo da telecomunicação, o calibre da 
neve, o ornithopter, o airphibian, e outro.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">esamina 16 invenzioni: il sommergibile, la radio 
della batteria, la sgranatrice, il reaper, il microscopio elettronico,
il telefono, il grammofono, il cavo di telecomunicazione, il calibro 
della neve, il ornithopter, il airphibian ed altri.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">εξετάζει 16 εφευρέσεις: το υποβρύχιο, το 
ραδιόφωνο μπαταριών, το τζιν βαμβακιού, ο θεριστής, το 
ηλεκτρονικό μικροσκόπιο, το τηλέφωνο, gramophone, το καλώδιο 
τηλεπικοινωνιών, ο μετρητής χιονιού, ornithopter, airphibian,
και άλλοι.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">examina 16 invenciones: el submarino, la radio de la
batería, la ginebra de algodón, el reaper, el microscopio 
electrónico, el teléfono, el gramófono, el cable de la 
telecomunicación, la galga de la nieve, el ornithopter, el 
airphibian, y otros.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κοινωνικές επιστήμες</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
